{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-022","title":"左邻右舍","sectionId":"chapter-02","sectionTitle":"日常交际你最强","pageStart":133,"pageEnd":138,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":16,"duplicateEntryCount":22,"pages":[{"number":133,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"22 左邻右舍"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"neighbour [ˈneɪbə(r)]","headword":"neighbour"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.邻居"},{"type":"note","text":"◎next-door neighbour隔壁邻居"},{"type":"entry","text":"neighbourhood [ˈneɪbəhʊd]","headword":"neighbourhood"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.附近；街坊"},{"type":"note","text":"◎neighbourhood committee居委会"}]},{"number":134,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"resident student寄宿生，住校生","headword":"resident student"},{"type":"entry","text":"acquaintance [əˈkweɪntəns]","headword":"acquaintance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.熟人"},{"type":"note","text":"◎make acquaintance with与…相识"},{"type":"entry","text":"nodding acquaintance点头之交","headword":"nodding acquaintance"},{"type":"entry","text":"visit [ˈvɪzɪt]","headword":"visit"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v. 拜访"},{"type":"note","text":"◎pay a visit to拜访"},{"type":"entry","text":"character [ˈkærəktə(r)]","headword":"character"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.性格"},{"type":"entry","text":"easygoing [ˌiːziˈgəʊɪŋ]","headword":"easygoing"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.随和的"}]},{"number":135,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"◎easygoing parents随和的父母"},{"type":"entry","text":"gentle [ˈdʒentl]","headword":"gentle"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.温和的"},{"type":"entry","text":"friendly [ˈfrendli]","headword":"friendly"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.友好的"}]},{"number":136,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"get along with 与…和睦相处","headword":"get along with"},{"type":"entry","text":"loud [laʊd]","headword":"loud"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.吵闹的"},{"type":"entry","text":"rigidly [ˈrɪdʒɪdli]","headword":"rigidly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.严格地"},{"type":"note","text":"◎rigidly prohibit严格禁止"}]},{"number":137,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"backbiting [ˌbækˈbaɪtiŋ]","headword":"backbiting"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.背后诽谤"},{"type":"entry","text":"violent [ˈvaɪələnt]","headword":"violent"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.暴力的；猛烈的"},{"type":"entry","text":"make trouble 闹事","headword":"make trouble"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：How's your new home? （你的新家怎么样？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：My neighbour plays rock music all night every night.（我的邻居"},{"type":"text","text":"每天都整晚放摇滚乐。）"}]},{"number":138,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Do you know this girl? （你认识这个女孩吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：No, but I often see her when I run in my neighbourhood.（不认"},{"type":"text","text":"识，但我在家附近跑步时经常能见到她。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Why did the couple next door quarrel? （隔壁那对夫妇为什么吵"},{"type":"text","text":"架？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：It was sparked off by a joke. But the wife thought it was"},{"type":"text","text":"disrespectful.（因为一句玩笑。但是那位妻子觉得那样说很无礼。）"}]}]}